<h2 id="geojson">GeoJSON</h2>

<h3 id="convert-various-formats-to-geojson">Convert various formats to geojson</h3>

<p>From a <code class="highlighter-rouge">numeric</code> vector of length 2</p>

<p>as <em>json</em></p>

<div class="language-r highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">geojson_json</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nf">c</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="m">32.45</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="m">-99.74</span><span class="p">))</span><span class="w">
